:"text","value":"有时候手机上需要创建一个新知识库整理旧知识库的内容，或者给缺少权限的同事授权，还得跑去电脑端操作，非常耽误时间。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"PSlC7h0iVA"}],"key":"CwpaHxkapH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"手机端登录网页版，并且调整到桌面模式可以解决这个问题。特别注意，手机网页和手机 App 是一样的接口。如果在电脑网页创建知识库以后，自动跳转到手机页面会打不开，要再手动点击“请求桌面网页”。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"kMAakDlCnp"}],"key":"nbsOr7pljc"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其他问题多了去了，下次再吐槽。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"CFqqszAckk"}],"key":"YZksTsF7Kb"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文档","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"PjR6YHjZYa"}],"key":"C3JPd47ArY"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"编辑器各种奇奇怪怪的问题非常多。吞文字啊丢文字啊乱跑啊，在手机端上问题也非常多。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"iT6UiTMUq8"}],"key":"uNzwocn5SR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"电脑端的问题是，有时候在 App 内部，有时候跳转到网页。真不知道这个草台班子逻辑是怎么搞出来的。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"pQPldUh721"}],"key":"mcMUAMAqE7"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"吹的天花乱坠的飞书文档，稳定性和腾讯文档也就是半斤八两吧。写个文档还不够耽误时间的。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"GipvBdmHjY"}],"key":"SQcc5S3W82"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"素材2","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"IDiTbHdAXY"}],"identifier":"id-2","label":"素材2","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"ErRaZnkmXj"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因为飞书的那个任务不太好用，所以我很少直接用那个东西。然后如果你需要跟其他人协作的话，可以在这个群里边插入一些飞书任务。嗯，就是把那个任务要点转成那个飞书任务，啊，这样的话它就可以呃变成一个任务，在任务清单里面，然后提醒呀、关系人啊，就是指指派人啊，这就都可以用","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"mN3Sxk1zHg"}],"key":"N4f1tnbzs7"}],"key":"sfhDl1hCba"}],"key":"OSzDe8nEIl"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}